      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait r u sure? it really hurts when i move around or even just walk. i'm a bit worried it might be something more than just cramps though. if i take the codeine and it makes me super drowsy, is that a bad sign or just the medicine working? i don't really want to go to the hospital if i don't have to, it's so expensive and the wait times in sydney are insane right now.",
